name: Logohype Vol 1.0
description:
Spin King Logohype Vol1.0 Tee After much anticipation during the best part of 2013 our new flagship logotype shirts are now in stock and printed using the finest inks on the Anvil brand of cotton tee. Eye popping 3 colour graffiti style print on a superfine tight weave 100% cotton tee. Shirts come with exclusive new sleeve and neck labels now featured on all our tees. EU Size Guide (to fit chest):
  • Small 36" (90cm)
  • Medium 40" (100cm)
  • Large 44" (110cm)
  • Large 48" (120cm)
**Price includes free shipping to the UK**

name: Bean Fixed 2013/4 Reprint T-shirt
description:
Bean Fixed reprint tees for the coming 2014! **New in stock** Our beloved comedy value Bean Fixed t-shirts are finally back in stock! Designed exclusively for the fixed gear scene available in classic white, and now printed on the Gildan Ultra 100% cotton brand of tee. New for 2013/4! A2 Size prints with new Sleeve and neck labels! Price includes free shipping within the UK and to the States. EU Size Guide (to fit chest):
  • Small 34-36" (85-90cm)
  • Medium 38-40" (95-100cm)
  • Large 42-44" (105-110cm)
  • Large 46-48" (115-120cm)

name: Spin King Clothing Planet Tee in Grey
description:
The new flagship Spin King Planet tees are here! These water-based shirts are screen printed on the silky smooth Gildan Premium Heavyweight cotton t-shirt. Our new Spin King tee comes with cool new features such as the printed sleeve label, double sided woven label on the opposing sleeve, neck label on the outside rear of the tee and interior stitched woven size label. Stocks are limited so order early to avoid disappointment. Price includes free delivery to the UK and the US with free gifts to boot! EU Size Guide (to fit chest):
  • Small 34-36" (85-90cm)
  • Medium 38-40" (95-100cm)
  • Large 42-44" (105-110cm)

name: <b>Ryoto Fixed<b> Crank Design T-Shirt
description:

Currently available in white on Gildan Soft-Style t-shirt with more colours to come. The UK Price includes free shipping to mainland UK using standard Royal Mail 1st class delivery.
